---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Welkom">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#07153b] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-yellow-400"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 -left-10 w-80 h-80 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="text-white">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-yellow-400/20 border border-yellow-400/40 text-yellow-300 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-5 uppercase tracking-wide">
          Secundair onderwijs · Alsemberg
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-5">
          Groeien, leren en<br/>
          <span class="text-yellow-400">thuiskomen</span><br/>
          in Sint-Victor
        </h1>
        <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
          Wij zijn een katholieke school met meer dan 150 jaar traditie. Hier voelt elke leerling zich welkom en uitgedaagd om het beste van zichzelf te worden.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="/inschrijvingen" class="bg-yellow-400 text-[#07153b] font-bold px-7 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-yellow-300 transition shadow-lg text-sm">
            Inschrijven 2026-2027
          </a>
          <a href="/sv-tamtam" class="bg-white/10 border border-white/30 text-white font-semibold px-7 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition text-sm">
            SV-Tamtam
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-end justify-center">
        <img
          src="/school-schets.png"
          alt="Schets van de schoolgebouwen van Sint-Victor Alsemberg"
          class="w-full max-w-2xl opacity-90 mix-blend-lighten"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Drie pijlers -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Onze aanpak</h2>
        <div class="w-14 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mx-auto mt-3 rounded-full"></div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mt-4 max-w-xl mx-auto">Drie woorden vatten samen waar Sint-Victor voor staat.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition border-t-4 border-[#07153b]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#07153b]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-[#07153b] text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">Warm</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#07153b] mb-3">Iedereen hoort erbij</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">We bouwen aan een sterke schoolgemeenschap waar elke leerling zich gezien en gewaardeerd voelt. Geen leerling valt uit de boot.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition border-t-4 border-[#07153b]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#07153b]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-[#07153b] text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">Sterk</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#07153b] mb-3">Leren met stevige basis</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Ambitieus onderwijs met aandacht voor elk leerpad. We bereiden leerlingen voor op hoger onderwijs én op het leven.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition border-t-4 border-[#07153b]">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#07153b]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="bg-[#07153b] text-yellow-400 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wide">Samen</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#07153b] mb-3">Ouders dichtbij</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">Ouders zijn welkome partners in het schoolgebeuren. Open communicatie via Smartschool en regelmatige contactmomenten.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Snel naar -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Snel naar</h2>
        <div class="w-14 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mx-auto mt-3 rounded-full"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <a href="/Infobrochure Sint-Victor 26-27.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:border-[#07153b] transition group text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-3">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#07153b] transition">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#07153b] group-hover:text-white transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="font-bold text-[#07153b] text-sm mb-1">Infobrochure</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">2026-2027</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/onze-school#visie" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:border-[#07153b] transition group text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-3">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#07153b] transition">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#07153b] group-hover:text-white transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="font-bold text-[#07153b] text-sm mb-1">Onze visie</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Waar staan we voor?</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/studieaanbod" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:border-[#07153b] transition group text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-3">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#07153b] transition">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#07153b] group-hover:text-white transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="font-bold text-[#07153b] text-sm mb-1">Studieaanbod</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Alle richtingen</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/schoolreglement" class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-gray-100 hover:border-[#07153b] transition group text-center">
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-3">
            <div class="bg-[#07153b]/10 rounded-xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#07153b] transition">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#07153b] group-hover:text-white transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="font-bold text-[#07153b] text-sm mb-1">Schoolreglement</div>
          <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">Regels & afspraken</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Praktisch -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b] mb-3">Praktisch</h2>
        <div class="w-14 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          {[
            { label: "Afwezigheid melden", href: "/afwezigheden" },
            { label: "Infobrochure 2026-2027 (PDF)", href: "/Infobrochure Sint-Victor 26-27.pdf", extern: true },
            { label: "Chromebookproject", href: "/chromebookproject" },
            { label: "Schoolreglement", href: "/schoolreglement" },
            { label: "FAQ — veelgestelde vragen", href: "/faq" },
            { label: "SV-Tamtam nieuwskrantjes", href: "/sv-tamtam" },
          ].map(l => (
            <a href={l.href} target={l.extern ? "_blank" : undefined} rel={l.extern ? "noopener" : undefined} class="flex items-center justify-between bg-white rounded-xl px-5 py-4 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-transparent hover:border-[#07153b] transition group">
              <span class="font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-[#07153b] text-sm transition">{l.label}</span>
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-[#07153b] transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b] mb-3">Digitale tools</h2>
        <div class="w-14 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mb-8 rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a href="https://sv.smartschool.be" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-transparent hover:border-[#07153b] transition group">
            <div class="rounded-xl w-12 h-12 shrink-0 overflow-hidden">
              <img src="/smartschool-logo.png" alt="Smartschool" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-[#07153b] text-sm">Smartschool</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">sv.smartschool.be · digitaal leerplatform</div>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-[#07153b] ml-auto transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://instagram.com/sintvictor" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-transparent hover:border-pink-400 transition group">
            <div class="rounded-xl w-12 h-12 shrink-0 overflow-hidden">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
                <defs>
                  <radialGradient id="ig-grad" cx="30%" cy="107%" r="150%">
                    <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffd676"/>
                    <stop offset="25%" stop-color="#f2a454"/>
                    <stop offset="45%" stop-color="#f05c3c"/>
                    <stop offset="60%" stop-color="#c2275e"/>
                    <stop offset="80%" stop-color="#8b3a8f"/>
                    <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4c5bce"/>
                  </radialGradient>
                </defs>
                <rect width="48" height="48" rx="12" fill="url(#ig-grad)"/>
                <rect x="13" y="13" width="22" height="22" rx="6" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"/>
                <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="5.5" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2.5"/>
                <circle cx="35" cy="13" r="1.8" fill="white"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">Instagram</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">@sintvictor · schoolleven in beelden</div>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-pink-400 ml-auto transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://facebook.com/sintvictor" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-transparent hover:border-blue-500 transition group">
            <div class="rounded-xl w-12 h-12 shrink-0 overflow-hidden">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full h-full">
                <rect width="48" height="48" rx="12" fill="#1877F2"/>
                <path d="M26.5 25.5h3.2l0.6-4H26.5v-2.2c0-1.1 0.5-2.1 2.2-2.1h1.7V13.4c0 0-1.5-0.3-3-0.3-3.1 0-5.1 1.9-5.1 5.2v3.2H19v4h3.3V36h4.2V25.5z" fill="white"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">Facebook</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">@sintvictor · nieuws & evenementen</div>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-blue-500 ml-auto transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@SintVictorAlsemberg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
            class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md border border-transparent hover:border-red-500 transition group">
            <div class="bg-red-600 rounded-xl w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 00-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 00.502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 002.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 002.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-bold text-gray-800 text-sm">YouTube</div>
              <div class="text-gray-400 text-xs">@SintVictorAlsemberg · video's & reportages</div>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-300 group-hover:text-red-500 ml-auto transition" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SV-Tamtam nieuws -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-10">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">SV-Nieuws</h2>
          <div class="w-14 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mt-3 rounded-full"></div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3">Het laatste nieuws uit onze school</p>
        </div>
        
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {[
          { datum: "20 mei 2026", tag: "Inschrijvingen", titel: "Inschrijvingen 2026-2027", tekst: "De inschrijfperiode loopt van 20/05 tot 16/06/2026. Op 29 mei organiseren we op school de inschrijvingen voor nieuwe leerlingen van het 1ste jaar." },
          { datum: "29 april 2026", tag: "Evenement", titel: "Opendeurdag zaterdag 9 mei", tekst: "Kom onze school ontdekken! Van 9u tot 12u stellen we alle studierichtingen voor. Leerlingen en leerkrachten tonen je rond." },
          { datum: "18 april 2026", tag: "SV-Tamtam", titel: "14de editie SV-Tamtam beschikbaar", tekst: "De nieuwste editie van ons schoolmagazine staat klaar. Boordevol reportages, interviews en foto's van het schoolleven." },
        ].map(b => (
          <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition group border border-gray-100">
            <div class="h-1.5 bg-[#07153b] group-hover:bg-yellow-400 transition-colors"></div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
                <span class="bg-blue-50 text-[#07153b] text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">{b.tag}</span>
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-xs">{b.datum}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-[#07153b] text-base mb-2 leading-snug">{b.titel}</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">{b.tekst}</p>
              <a href="/sv-tamtam" class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[#07153b] text-xs font-semibold hover:underline">
                Lees meer <svg class="w-3 h-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Instagram feed -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-[#07153b]">Volg ons op Instagram</h2>
        <div class="w-14 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mx-auto mt-3 rounded-full"></div>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/sintvictor" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[#07153b] font-semibold hover:underline">@sintvictor</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <script src="https://snapwidget.com/js/snapwidget.js"></script>
      <iframe src="https://snapwidget.com/embed/897537" class="snapwidget-widget" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; width:100%; height:860px;"></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#07153b] py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-3">Klaar om deel uit te maken van Sint-Victor?</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Schrijf je in voor schooljaar 2026-2027 of kom langs tijdens onze opendeurdag op 16 mei.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/inschrijvingen" class="bg-yellow-400 text-[#07153b] font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-yellow-300 transition">Inschrijven</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
